text: Cnemaspis mumpuniae is a species of gecko from Pulau Natuna Besar, Indonesia. ==References== ==Further reading== *Amarasinghe, AA Thasun, et al. Wood Jr. "Cyrtodactylus rosichonariefi sp. nov.(Squamata: Gekkonidae), a new swamp-dwelling bent-toed gecko from Bunguran Island (Great Natuna), Indonesia." Zootaxa 3964.1 (2015): 114–124. title: Cnemaspis mumpuniae
